cast.overview: Debbie Ocean, a criminal mastermind, gathers a crew of female thieves to pull off the heist of the century at New York's annual Met Gala.
cast.title: Ocean's Eight

details.biography: Born and raised in Brooklyn, NY, Nathanya is a graduate of LaGuardia High School of Music & Art and Performing Arts. Shortly after graduating, she booked a role in Warner Bros "Oceans 8" playing the cool teen hacker "Veronica" where she starred alongside Rihanna, Sandra Bullock, and Sarah Paulson. She can be seen on the new HBO Max series "Generation" playing "Arianna".
details.name: Nathanya Alexander
